{"tid":1534890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"假如太子站真係有手足死左 我要香港人永遠記住","createTime":"2019-09-03T07:02:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T11:39:00.000Z","uid":185762,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"89c9a964c42204e6ada5baaa507290005412855d","tid":1534890,"uid":185762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:02:15.000Z","msg":"一篇新聞 一個連登post <br />\n可能有人反對 覺得你係作故仔<br />\n隨住時間過去 冇人推post就會沉底<br />\n有更大件事就會令大家忘記<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但係一個鬼故 一件不斷發生嘅靈異事件<br />\n係更容易令人記住 無論黃絲藍絲中立撚</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n就好似彩虹嘅鬼門關 當年日佔時期嘅鬼故<br />\n吊頸嶺等等<br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉 等大家討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bda75d41750c0c2719d2563ca212231f26a3a11","tid":1534890,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:02:50.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e459cbdc37a1220cb106deafede3afd111c4da74","tid":1534890,"uid":185762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:03:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"277ae8569b707dfab42ee09f13c97a16356ffbe5","tid":1534890,"uid":285855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:05:19.000Z","msg":"香港回歸未定案嫁<br />\n<br />\n借一下位, 純手動po請見諒<br />\n話我個PO已完結P牌又一日只可開一個, 搵人幫下手唔該<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1534137/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1534137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n侵侵叫大陸還清朝債卷<br />\n大陸唔肯還都仲未知<br />\n佢話前朝,唔認佢要還<br />\n如果唔駛還,唔認,咁點解要還香港<br />\nbloomberg同台灣都有講, 點解香港無黎聲氣<br />\n還, 大陸還唔還得起<br />\n唔還我地仲係英殖地<br />\n就算還都應該係還俾有還錢的政府, 我地就係台灣人<br />\n應該還俾承認的一個政權<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-29/trump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-08-29%2Ftrump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFFgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=71ee98c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-29/trump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zdS50W9Aq_Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzdS50W9Aq_Y&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFFgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=dcce13a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zdS50W9Aq_Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7RnZZ8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7RnZZ8.png&h=a10eff3b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"304fda68ff2f30409fd75d2f3bbe25e56d3c0ef5","tid":1534890,"uid":185762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:09:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1408828a6c95b55efc9190324d560bd10f8a5ca2","tid":1534890,"uid":124330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:20:10.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/boun